Release DevBuild 1.11 for 3.0

Settings Support + LanguagePack Changes
This means you can modify background image, language, and Modify the Primary and Secondary colors of Material Theme. Note that JS mods wont support switching over to another language.

Background Color Support
This means you can enable/disable rainbow background ;)

JavaScript Docs Redone
As you can tell, addJS() has been deprecated and has since been replaced with OpenAudioAPI.getJS() instead. Check OAM-APIs.js on how to use this function.

Snow redone + errorPages redone
* Found a better JS library for snow and is friendly to mobile devices * ErrorPages will now stop all sounds currently playing. * Console messages for settings now in place
Added Spanish and Hawaiian to Language Settings
Random Colors Match Holidays

Snow was over everything

Updated SweetAlert 2 to 7.0.5
Took a long time since there were alot of breaking changes involving inputs

YouTube Function will warn when you use full URL
This is a good testing tool, but a warning will be there as idiot proof. Hope this clears half the confusion.

Added metadata.json to work with OA+
Sorta useless, but ok :/
Fixed fading audio not working + own system (WIP)

Fixed Ambiance sound not stopping on region call
This should fix that, plus went back to old fade handler since the issue was destroying sound too early.
Fixed ambiance never calling YouTube or StackStorage URLs.
